Title: Guelph

Guelph

Distinct, resilient, and bold, Guelph is a centre for innovation, creation, and community. Guelph has a strong value proposition for business investment owing to its geographic location, vibrant downtown, access to talent, research expertise and daily rail service. It is a community that embraces and drives progressive social and circular business models. Guelph is located along the Innovation Corridor, the largest tech cluster in North America, with more than 15,000 tech companies, including 5,000+ startups, and nearly 300,000 employees in high-tech industries.

With incubators, accelerators, research institutes, and maker-mentality, it is a global maker hub of ambitious and highly-trained people. It is also one of the top 25 startup ecosystems in the world with a startup density second only to Silicon Valley.
